             was indicted for <rs id="t18171203-132-off703" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18171203-132-off703" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18171203-132-off703" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18171203-132-cd704" type="crimeDate">2d of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18171203-132-off703 t18171203-132-cd704"></join>, one watch, value 30s.; one chain, value 1s.; one seal, value 1s. 6d.; and one key, value 2d., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18171203-132-victim963" type="victimName">
                           David Joseph 
                           Morrice
                        <interp inst="t18171203-132-victim963" type="surname" value="Morrice"></interp>
